Package io.github.yvasyliev.forwarder.telegram.bot.configuration

package io.github.yvasyliev.forwarder.telegram.bot.configuration
Contains configuration classes for the Telegram Forwarder Bot. This package is responsible for setting up the application's configuration, including properties, beans, and other necessary components.
